  "texts": [
    "SIEM systems provide a dashboard to monitor the organization's security posture in real time.",
    "Dashboards often include visualization of the data in the form of charts, graphs, and widgets.",
    "Reports can be generated regularly or on demand for compliance, incident analysis, and executive summaries.",
    "The dashboard also shows alerts generated by the correlation engine when a security incident or suspicious activity is identified.",
    "Alerts can trigger notifications, such as emails, SMS messages, or integrations with incident response systems."
  ],
